    "description": "This prawn curry is typical to Goa, south India. It has a caramelised red onion, curry spice and coconut cream base with a salty-sweet depth from our incredible juicy king prawns. Enhanced with fish sauce, lifted with fresh coriander and lime, all served over buttery cinnamon rice, need we Go'an?",
